loginToAccountDescription: Please enter your account and password to continue
numberSegmentPlaceHolder: Multiple, seperated or one per line, up to 100 at a time
uploadNote1: Note: No matter whether the number in the number file has a country code or not, the country code must be selected
uploadNote2: Note: Numbers uploaded in each batch can only be numbers from the same country, and analytics of numbers from multiple countries at one time is not supported.
uploadNote3: Note: After analytics, the downloaded number system has already brought the country code.
uploadNote4: Note: The file format only supports TXT format files/one mobile phone number per line/minimum 2000-200W number package upload/file less than 30MB.
generateNote1: Note: This function is used to generate numbers in bulk, customize country codes and number ranges, and automatically generate the last few digits in order
generateNote2: Note: A single number segment, such as the country code set to 55, the number segment set to 3198353, and the last few digits set to 4, this function will generate ten thousand numbers from 5531983530000 to 5531983539999.
generateNote3: Note: Multiple number segments, such as the country code set to 55, the number segment set to 119771319835219951, and the last few digits set to 5, this function will generate three hundred thousand numbers from 5511977100000 to 551197719999553198350000 to 55319835999552199510000 to 5521995199999.
regionNote1: Note: The uploaded number must include the country code
regionNote2: Note: Numbers uploaded in each batch can only be numbers from the same country, and analytics of numbers from multiple countries at one time is not supported.
regionNote3: Note: The file format only supports TXT format files/one mobile phone number per line/minimum 100-200W number package upload/file less than 30MB.
oldPasswordDesc: Please enter the original login password
newUserNameDesc: Please enter the new username as you want
newPasswordDesc: The new password must be greater than 6 characters
confirmPasswordDesc: Please enter the new password again
genErrMsg: An unexpected error occured while generating phone numbers
compareNote1: Please upload two phone numbers file.
compareNote2: System will detect the same number from first and second file.
compareNote3: Then it will be downloaded automatically.
